                                         JOHANNESBURG â€“ Another African National Congress (ANC) municipal official has been killed in KwaZulu-Natal.  Nkosinathi Ngcobo was shot dead last night. His murder brings to five the number of ANC officials killed in the Harry Gwala region. In July, former ANC Youth League national secretary-general, Sindiso Magaqa, and two other ANC members were shot in an apparent ambush in the same district. Magaqa succumbed to his wounds last month.